<!-- Moved from templates/posts/default.php -->

    <div><p>Publishers <a title="Companies > Ubisoft [1,310 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/companies/ubisoft">Ubisoft</a> and <a title="Companies > Hooded Horse [14 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/companies/hooded-horse">Hooded Horse</a>, and developer <a title="Companies > Unfrozen [3 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/companies/unfrozen">Unfrozen</a> have delayed the Early Access release of turn-based <a title="Genres > Strategy [287 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/genres/strategy">strategy game</a> <em><a title="Games > Heroes of Might and Magic: Olden Era [3 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/games/heroes-of-might-and-magic-olden-era">Heroes of Might and Magic: Olden Era</a></em> from its <a href="https://www.gematsu.com/2025/07/heroes-of-might-and-magic-olden-era-to-be-published-by-hooded-horse">previously planned</a> 2025 release window to 2026. It will be available for <a title="Platforms > PC [24,491 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/pc">PC</a> via <a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/3105440/Heroes_of_Might_and_Magic_Olden_Era/" target="_blank">Steam</a>. <span id="more-999096"></span></p><p>A new demo is also available now, which features four playable factions and three different game modes—Classic, Single Hero mode, and Arena mode. While the demo is single-player only, the full game will feature <a title="Genres > Multiplayer [615 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/genres/multiplayer">multiplayer</a>, additional modes, and more factions.</p><p>Watch a new trailer below.</p><h2><span>Demo Trailer</span></h2><p><iframe title="Heroes of Might &amp; Magic: Olden Era — Demo AVAILABLE NOW!" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/AyfsDzLdz_w?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen=""></iframe></p></div>

        
    
